{"tid":1429134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港人舉美國旗被Trump Endorse！】下次拎支美國旗出嚟，支持美國國會通過香港人權及民主法案！","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:59:39.000Z","uid":14328,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"92a70b10df11bff9a7fe2a132a1089705d86a190","tid":1429134,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/07/gM2Dx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2FgM2Dx6.png&h=854e9bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國人普遍對香港人拎美國旗出嚟示威，持正面態度。<br />\n<br />\n而家連President Trump 都出聲表揚<br />\n仲要有美國人話：不如將香港加做美國５１區<br />\n<br />\n我覺得下次遊行，不如拎支美國國旗出嚟，格離有手足舉牌，用英文寫：<br />\n「支持美國國會通過香港人權及民主法案！」<br />\n「We support Donald Trump, Please liberate Hong Kong!」<br />\n之類。<br />\n<br />\n希望可以作為一個推力，令美國國會係１１月之前通過香港人權及民主法案，通過左之後，中國一定好撚大獲！"},{"pid":"8ebda3c55126c13af236e280d3137b93a5d39436","tid":1429134,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1877d2a893fcc63af226df01ea302990bb0cb8","tid":1429134,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"3e852366b9533bc943a9d36a415662673dbf8e93","tid":1429134,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:23:34.000Z","msg":"唔係侵，係佢d fans"},{"pid":"1a129cd0c7e539c624011490f9a336eeb7cc95c0","tid":1429134,"uid":276807,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"可唔可以寫 US Congress 唔好寫 Trump<br />\n呢個唔係佢官方 page<br />\n人地話 Hong Kong is a part of China<br />\n有好多議員都好憎 Trump 你寫 Trump 唔會號召到佢地"},{"pid":"c295f6b07e8ddac902c4092e2b708fb5217c6d80","tid":1429134,"uid":145043,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"Area 51 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dan